{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_decision", "label": "Decision: ESLint independiente por aplicaci\u00f3n (ADR-001)", "file_type": "rationale", "rationale": "El Bloque C (especificaci\u00f3n oficial) propon\u00eda un packages/shared-config con ESLint compartido entre backend y frontend. Pero al generar apps/backend con Nest CLI 11 y apps/frontend con create-next-app (Next.js 16), ambos frameworks producen configuraciones ESLint flat-config (eslint.config.mjs) con bases mutuamente incompatibles: NestJS 11 usa typescript-eslint + eslint-plugin-prettier/recommended, mientras Next.js 16 usa eslint-config-next (reglas propias de Core Web Vitals, React y a11y). Forzar un preset legacy \u00fanico (.eslintrc con extends) habr\u00eda degradado las reglas oficiales de ambos frameworks y generado fricci\u00f3n en cada actualizaci\u00f3n futura. Por eso se decidi\u00f3 mantener eslint.config.mjs independiente y sin abstracci\u00f3n por cada app, compartiendo desde packages/shared-config \u00fanicamente prettier.config.js y tsconfig.base.json (como referencia de estilo, no como config real forzada). Consecuencia aceptada: las reglas de lint pueden divergir levemente entre backend y frontend, a cambio de no pelear contra las herramientas oficiales; se reevaluar\u00e1 si ambos ecosistemas convergen en el futuro.", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_nestjs_cli_11", "label": "Nest CLI 11", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_nextjs_16", "label": "Next.js 16 (create-next-app)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_typescript_eslint", "label": "typescript-eslint", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_eslint_plugin_prettier", "label": "eslint-plugin-prettier/recommended", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_eslint_config_next", "label": "eslint-config-next", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_shared_config_pkg", "label": "packages/shared-config", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_prettier_config", "label": "prettier.config.js (shared)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_decisions_adr_001_eslint_independiente_por_app_tsconfig_base", "label": "tsconfig.base.json (shared reference)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/decisions/ADR-001-eslint-independiente-por-app.md", "source_location": null, "source_ur